flowchart LR
  F[Uploaded File CSV or Excel] --> V[Validate File]
  V --> DF[Pandas DataFrame]
  DF --> P[Schema plus Stats]
  DF --> C[Create Row/Column Context]
  C --> E[Gemini Embeddings]
  E --> IDX[FAISS Index]
  P --> PR[Prompt = Question plus Schema plus Context]
  IDX --> R[Retrieve Relevant Context]
  R --> PR
  PR --> LLM[Selected LLM] --> A[Grounded Answer]
